---
// src/pages/about.astro
export const prerender = true;
import PostLayout from '../layouts/PostLayout.astro';
---

<PostLayout
  title="關於"
  lang="zh-TW"
  description="Vincent Xu — 財務官轉工程師，自學程式、共同創辦島島阿學，現在在 AI × 產品的邊界工作。攀岩、衝浪、咖啡。"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="zh-TW" href="https://quidproquo.cc/about" />
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://quidproquo.cc/en/about" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </Fragment>

  <div class="content about-page">
    <div class="about-grid">

      <!-- ── Left sidebar ── -->
      <aside class="about-sidebar">
        <div class="about-sidebar-inner">
          <p class="about-sidebar-name">Vincent<br />Xu</p>
          <p class="about-sidebar-title">AI Agent Engineer</p>
          <p class="about-sidebar-blurb">做 AI 與產品，把想法做成真正能幫助別人的東西。</p>
          <div class="about-sidebar-rule"></div>
          <nav class="about-sidebar-nav">
            <a href="https://github.com/vincentxuu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.58 2 12.23c0 4.52 2.87 8.36 6.84 9.72.5.1.68-.22.68-.49 0-.24-.01-1.03-.01-1.87-2.78.62-3.37-1.2-3.37-1.2-.45-1.18-1.11-1.5-1.11-1.5-.91-.64.07-.63.07-.63 1 .07 1.53 1.06 1.53 1.06.9 1.58 2.35 1.12 2.92.86.09-.67.35-1.12.63-1.38-2.22-.26-4.56-1.15-4.56-5.1 0-1.13.39-2.05 1.03-2.77-.1-.26-.45-1.31.1-2.73 0 0 .85-.28 2.78 1.06A9.4 9.4 0 0 1 12 6.9c.85 0 1.71.12 2.51.35 1.92-1.34 2.77-1.06 2.77-1.06.55 1.42.21 2.47.1 2.73.64.72 1.03 1.64 1.03 2.77 0 3.96-2.34 4.83-4.57 5.09.36.32.68.95.68 1.92 0 1.39-.01 2.5-.01 2.85 0 .27.18.6.69.49A10.25 10.25 0 0 0 22 12.23C22 6.58 17.52 2 12 2Z"/></svg>
              <span>GitHub</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/vincent-xu-333b7a67/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6.94 8.5A1.56 1.56 0 1 1 6.93 5.4a1.56 1.56 0 0 1 .01 3.1ZM5.6 9.67h2.68V18H5.6V9.67Zm4.36 0h2.57v1.14h.04c.36-.68 1.23-1.4 2.53-1.4 2.7 0 3.2 1.84 3.2 4.22V18h-2.68v-3.88c0-.92-.02-2.1-1.24-2.1-1.25 0-1.44.99-1.44 2.03V18H9.96V9.67Z"/></svg>
              <span>LinkedIn</span>
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:vincent.xu.work@gmail.com">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 6.5h16A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 21.5 8v8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 20 17.5H4A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 2.5 16V8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4 6.5Zm0 1.5v.2l8 5.17 8-5.17V8H4Zm16 8V9.96l-7.59 4.91a.75.75 0 0 1-.82 0L4 9.96V16h16Z"/></svg>
              <span>Email</span>
            </a>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <!-- ── Right content ── -->
      <div class="about-body">
        <h1 class="about-h1">關於我</h1>

        <h2 class="about-section-h2"><span class="about-now-label"><span class="live-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>現在</span></h2>
        <ul class="about-now-list">
          <li><span class="about-now-text">在 <a href="https://maiagent.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MaiAgent</a> 做 AI Agent 開發，處理真實企業場景裡的 workflow 與落地問題</span></li>
          <li><span class="about-now-text">和夥伴一起經營 <a href="https://daodao.so/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">島島阿學</a>，把自主學習做成能持續發生的產品</span></li>
          <li><span class="about-now-text">持續打造 <a href="https://nobodyclimb.cc/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">NobodyClimb</a>，記錄攀岩社群與路線故事</span></li>
          <li><span class="about-now-text">寫這個部落格，整理 AI、產品、學習與實作裡真正想過的事</span></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="about-prose">
          <p class="about-intro-lede">
            我的路徑不典型：財務官、教育工作者、共同創辦島島阿學、自學轉職工程師，到 AI Agent 開發。回頭看，主軸其實只有一條：持續學、持續做，讓抽象的想法變成能真的幫到人的東西。
          </p>

          <div class="about-timeline" aria-label="職涯時間線">
            <div class="about-timeline-item">
              <div class="about-timeline-year">2014–2019</div>
              <div class="about-timeline-content">
                <h3>軍中財務官</h3>
                <p>管薪資、審憑證、跑預算。這段時間養成了我對流程、細節與執行落地的敏感。</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-timeline-item">
              <div class="about-timeline-year">2019–2021</div>
              <div class="about-timeline-content">
                <h3>轉到教育現場</h3>
                <p>在台東做教育，也進入實驗教育工作者培育計畫。那時我開始真正碰到「學習為什麼這麼難」這個問題。</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-timeline-item">
              <div class="about-timeline-year">2020</div>
              <div class="about-timeline-content">
                <h3>共同創辦島島阿學</h3>
                <p>因為想解決學習資源不平等的問題，我決定自學程式，自己把想法實踐出來。</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-timeline-item">
              <div class="about-timeline-year">2023–Now</div>
              <div class="about-timeline-content">
                <h3>工程師 / AI Agent 開發</h3>
                <p>轉職做工程師，是因為我發現這份工作很適合我：需要持續學習，也一直有新的挑戰，同時能帶來很直接的成就感。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="about-notes">
            <div class="about-principles" aria-label="principles">
              <p><strong>學習</strong>不是囤積知識，是改變思考方式。</p>
              <p><strong>產品</strong>不是堆功能，是理解人怎麼行動。</p>
              <p><strong><em>Quid pro quo</em></strong>：把真正做過、想過的東西整理成別人也能用的形式，然後多給一點。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-offwork">
              <div class="about-offwork-tags" aria-label="outside of work">
                <span class="about-offwork-tag">攀岩</span>
                <span class="about-offwork-tag">衝浪</span>
                <span class="about-offwork-tag">手沖咖啡</span>
              </div>
              <p>我喜歡這些事的直接，也喜歡它們帶來的挑戰。它們很誠實，也很能反映一個人怎麼面對自己。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="about-section-h2">Projects</h2>
        <div class="about-projects">
          <div class="project-card">
            <div class="project-header">
              <span class="project-name">島島阿學 DaoDao</span>
              <span class="project-badge">共同創辦人</span>
            </div>
            <p class="project-desc">
              陪伴自主學習者從「想學」到真正完成目標、體驗學習成就感的社群平台，致力打造自主學習的生態圈。透過公開實踐、共同挑戰、AI 推薦，讓學習進展看得見、讓行動持續發生。榮獲 g0v 公民科技競賽與親子天下教育創新 100 獎。
            </p>
            <div class="project-tags">
              <span class="ptag">Product</span>
              <span class="ptag">Behavioral Design</span>
              <span class="ptag">Node.js</span>
              <span class="ptag">Next.js</span>
              <span class="ptag">RAG</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-links">
              <a href="https://daodao.so/" class="project-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">官網 →</a>
              <a href="https://app.daodao.so/" class="project-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">產品 →</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/daodaoedu/daodao" class="project-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub →</a>
              <a href="/posts/product/2026-03-12-daodao-product-design" class="project-link">文章 →</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="project-card">
            <div class="project-header">
              <span class="project-name">NobodyClimb</span>
              <span class="project-badge">Side Project</span>
            </div>
            <p class="project-desc">
              攀岩社群平台，讓每個攀岩人的故事留下來。台灣攀岩社群正在快速成長，但沒有一個地方真正屬於這群人——NobodyClimb 想填補這個空缺，讓每一段路線、每一次突破、每一個人的旅程都有地方被記住。
            </p>
            <div class="project-tags">
              <span class="ptag">Community</span>
              <span class="ptag">Cloudflare Workers</span>
              <span class="ptag">LangGraph</span>
              <span class="ptag">RAG</span>
              <span class="ptag">React Native</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-links">
              <a href="https://nobodyclimb.cc/" class="project-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">網站 →</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/vincentxuu/nobodyclimb" class="project-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub →</a>
              <a href="/posts/product/2026-03-12-nobodyclimb-product" class="project-link">文章 →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="about-section-h2">技能 & 工具</h2>
        <div class="about-skills">
          <div class="skill-row">
            <span class="skill-cat">Backend</span>
            <div class="skill-tags">
              <span class="tag-pill">Node.js</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">TypeScript</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Express.js</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Hono</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">FastAPI</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Python</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-row">
            <span class="skill-cat">Frontend</span>
            <div class="skill-tags">
              <span class="tag-pill">React</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Next.js</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">React Native</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">TailwindCSS</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Zustand</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">TanStack Query</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-row">
            <span class="skill-cat">Database</span>
            <div class="skill-tags">
              <span class="tag-pill">PostgreSQL</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">MySQL</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Redis</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">ClickHouse</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">D1 (SQLite)</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Qdrant</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-row">
            <span class="skill-cat">DevOps</span>
            <div class="skill-tags">
              <span class="tag-pill">Docker</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">GitHub Actions</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Cloudflare Workers</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Nginx</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">PM2</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-row">
            <span class="skill-cat">AI / ML</span>
            <div class="skill-tags">
              <span class="tag-pill">LangGraph</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">RAG Pipeline</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">LangChain</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Vectorize</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">LLM Evals</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Workers AI</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-row">
            <span class="skill-cat">AI 開發工具</span>
            <div class="skill-tags">
              <span class="tag-pill">Claude Code</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">GitHub Copilot</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Cursor</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">OpenSpec</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Codex</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-row">
            <span class="skill-cat">Product</span>
            <div class="skill-tags">
              <span class="tag-pill">Product Design</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">UX Research</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Figma</span>
              <span class="tag-pill">Community Building</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="about-section-h2">聯絡</h2>
        <div class="about-links">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/vincent-xu-333b7a67/" class="link-chip" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/>
              <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/>
              <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/>
            </svg>
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/vincentxuu" class="link-chip" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.477 2 12c0 4.418 2.865 8.166 6.839 9.489.5.092.682-.217.682-.482 0-.237-.009-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.604-3.369-1.342-3.369-1.342-.454-1.155-1.11-1.462-1.11-1.462-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.03 1.531 1.03.892 1.529 2.341 1.087 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.11-4.555-4.943 0-1.091.39-1.984 1.029-2.683-.103-.253-.446-1.27.098-2.647 0 0 .84-.269 2.75 1.025A9.578 9.578 0 0 1 12 6.836c.85.004 1.705.114 2.504.336 1.909-1.294 2.747-1.025 2.747-1.025.546 1.377.202 2.394.1 2.647.64.699 1.028 1.592 1.028 2.683 0 3.842-2.339 4.687-4.566 4.935.359.309.678.919.678 1.852 0 1.336-.012 2.415-.012 2.743 0 .267.18.578.688.48C19.138 20.163 22 16.418 22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10z"/>
            </svg>
            GitHub
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:vincent.xu.work@gmail.com" class="link-chip">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/>
              <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/>
            </svg>
            Email
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PostLayout>

<style is:global>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 900px;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* ── Sidebar ── */
  .about-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 5.5rem;
    align-self: start;
  }

  .about-sidebar-inner {
    padding-right: 2rem;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-sidebar-name {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--brand-900);
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .about-sidebar-title {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.09em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .about-sidebar-rule {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 0.9rem 0;
  }

  .about-sidebar-nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .about-sidebar-nav a {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.12s;
  }

  .about-sidebar-nav a:hover {
    color: var(--brand-500);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  /* ── Right body ── */
  .about-body {
    padding-left: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-h1 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--brand-900);
    margin: 0 0 1.4rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  /* Override global .content h2 for about page */
  .about-section-h2 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif !important;
    font-size: 1.4rem !important;
    font-weight: 400 !important;
    color: var(--brand-900) !important;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem !important;
    padding-bottom: 0.35rem !important;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border) !important;
    line-height: 1.2 !important;
    display: block !important;
    justify-content: unset !important;
  }

  .about-section-h2::after {
    display: none !important;
  }

  /* ── Intro lede ── */
  .about-intro-lede {
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--brand-500);
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  /* ── Pull quote ── */
  .about-pullquote {
    font-size: 0.95rem !important;
    line-height: 1.8 !important;
    color: var(--text-secondary) !important;
    background: var(--bg-subtle) !important;
    border: 1px solid var(--border) !important;
    border-radius: 8px !important;
    padding: 1rem 1.3rem !important;
    margin: 1.3rem 0 !important;
  }

  .about-pullquote em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--brand-500);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ── Now section ── */
  .about-now-label {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.55rem;
  }

  .about-now-list {
    list-style: none !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
    margin: 0 0 1.4rem !important;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .about-now-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    padding: 0.55rem 0.85rem;
    background: var(--bg-subtle);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  .about-now-list li::before {
    content: "→";
    color: var(--brand-500);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .about-now-list li:hover {
    border-color: var(--brand-500);
  }

  /* Live dot */
  .live-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--brand-500);
    display: inline-block;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    animation: live-pulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes live-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 var(--brand-500); }
    50% { opacity: 0.6; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px transparent; }
  }

  /* ── Projects ── */
  .about-projects {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-page .project-card {
    padding: 1rem 1.15rem;
    background: var(--bg-subtle);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--brand-500);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    transition: border-left-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
  }

  .about-page .project-card:hover {
    border-left-color: var(--heading-accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  .about-page .project-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .about-page .project-name {
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--brand-900);
  }

  .about-page .project-badge {
